title: Änimal "Pixelated Thoughts" - Converse Red Light Sessions
description: Indie electronica from production duo Änimal as they hook up with guest vocalist Iris van Lommerse and Lennart de Vries (on drums) to play an experimental Red Light Radio session at a former squat in the centre of Amsterdam.
